<h2 id="mp-tfa-h2" style="margin: 3px; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% rgb(206, 242, 224); font-family: inherit; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgb(163, 191, 177); text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0.2em 0.4em;"><span class="mw-headline" id="From_today.27s_featured_article">From today's featured article</span></h2>
