<h2 id="mp-itn-h2" style="margin: 3px; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% rgb(206, 223, 242); font-family: inherit; font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid rgb(163, 176, 191); text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0.2em 0.4em;"><span class="mw-headline" id="In_the_news">In the news</span></h2>
</td>
