<tr>
<td style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 2px 5px;">
<div id="mp-itn">
<div style="float: right; margin-left: 0.5em;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Comet-SidingSpring-Passing-PlanetMars-On-20141019-ArtistConcept-20140905.jpg" title="Artist's rendering of Comet Siding Spring's Mars approach"><img alt="Artist's rendering of Comet Siding Spring's Mars approach" src="100px-comet-sidingspring-passing-planetmars-on-20141019-artistconcept-20140905_cropped.jpg" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/17/Comet-SidingSpring-Passing-PlanetMars-On-20141019-ArtistConcept-20140905_cropped.jpg/150px-Comet-SidingSpring-Passing-PlanetMars-On-20141019-ArtistConcept-20140905_cropped.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/17/Comet-SidingSpring-Passing-PlanetMars-On-20141019-ArtistConcept-20140905_cropped.jpg/200px-Comet-SidingSpring-Passing-PlanetMars-On-20141019-ArtistConcept-20140905_cropped.jpg 2x" data-file-width="624" data-file-height="624" height="100" width="100"></a></div>
<ul>
<li><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C/2013_A1" title="C/2013 A1">Comet Siding Spring</a></b> makes a very close approach to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mars" title="Mars">Mars</a> <i>(artist's rendering pictured)</i> and is observed by means of surface rovers and satellites.</li>
<li>At least 41 people are killed in Nepal's worst <b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2014_Nepal_snowstorm_disaster" title="2014 Nepal snowstorm disaster">snowstorm disaster</a></b> around the mountains of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annapurna" title="Annapurna">Annapurna</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dhaulagiri" title="Dhaulagiri">Dhaulagiri</a>.</li>
<li><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Tirole" title="Jean Tirole">Jean Tirole</a></b> is awarded the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nobel_Memorial_Prize_in_Economic_Sciences" title="Nobel Memorial Prize in Economic Sciences">Nobel Memorial Prize in Economic Sciences</a> for his analysis of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Market_power" title="Market power">market power</a> and regulation.</li>
<li><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyclone_Hudhud" title="Cyclone Hudhud">Cyclone Hudhud</a></b> strikes India and Nepal, killing at least 84 people.</li>
<li><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evo_Morales" title="Evo Morales">Evo Morales</a></b> is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bolivian_general_election,_2014" title="Bolivian general election, 2014">re-elected</a> for a third term as <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/President_of_Bolivia" title="President of Bolivia">President of Bolivia</a>.</li>
<li><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kailash_Satyarthi" title="Kailash Satyarthi">Kailash Satyarthi</a></b> and <b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malala_Yousafzai" title="Malala Yousafzai">Malala Yousafzai</a></b> are awarded the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nobel_Peace_Prize" title="Nobel Peace Prize">Nobel Peace Prize</a> for their activism against the oppression of children and young people.</li>
</ul>
<p><b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portal:Current_events" title="Portal:Current events">Ongoing</a></b>: <span class="nowrap"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ebola_virus_epidemic_in_West_Africa" title="Ebola virus epidemic in West Africa">Ebola outbreak</a> –</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2014_Hong_Kong_protests" title="2014 Hong Kong protests">Hong Kong protests</a> –</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islamic_State_of_Iraq_and_the_Levant#October_2014" title="Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant">Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant</a></span><br>
<b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deaths_in_2014" title="Deaths in 2014">Recent deaths</a></b>: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gough_Whitlam" title="Gough Whitlam">Gough Whitlam</a></p>
</div>
